@wp.kernel

    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (tmp + wp.exp(0.75))
    v2 = wp.cos(0.72)
    v2 = 0.46
    v1 = v2
    tmp = wp.sin(wp.sin(wp.cos(v2 + 0.08)))
    v2 = wp.exp(((tmp + 0.42 + v0 + 0.87) - v0))
    data[tid] = v0
